snippet.title: Amber Heard  Elon Musk's ex flaunts boobs and booty in flesh flashing striptease
snippet.description:
31-year-old Amber Heard and Elon Musk, 46, in August, but she seems to be handling the single gal lifestyle like a pro.Just days after she was spotted cosying up to a mystery man on the Gold Coast, Australia, Amber Heard's Instagram was updated with a flesh-flashing video.

Inviting fans to get up-close-and-personal, the US beauty posed mid-pampering session alongside her trusty makeup artist and hairstylist.

Making sure to give her 567K followers a perv's eye view, the blonde bombshell wore a skintight white tank top and teeny shorts.She completed the revealing ensemble with a sky-high pair of patent black heels.

Having opted to ditch her bra in the relaxed setting, the Magic Mike XXL actress served major sideboob as she allowed her cleavage to roam free.

With a wine glass in one hand, the brazen vixen amped up the raunch factor, putting on a teasing display for the camera.

Perched on stool, the starlet embraced the 'up skirt' pose trend as she lifted her legs up and down in the air.Taking things a step further, another wrote: "I wish my face was that seat."

Stating the obvious, a straight-talking follower exclaimed: "SIDEBOOB."

Making reference to the Rum Diaries actress' peachiest ass-et, one happy customer wrote: "Booty," followed by two peach emojis.Clearly enjoying the one-woman peepshow, Amber — who divorced Johnny Depp earlier this year — opened her mouth and stared intently down the lens.

True to form, the silver screen siren's fans were quick to show their approval for the sizzling post, which has racked up close to 200,000 views in less than a day.

One awestruck viewer raved: "Those legs! Jesus," alongside several heart-eyed emojis.
